      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Chardonnay</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A clean Chardonnay reference for buyers who want texture without oak heaviness. It shows why Chardonnay can still feel sharp and mineral while doing more at the table than Sauvignon Blanc.</p>
    </div>
