      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Sauvignon Blanc</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A strong Sauvignon Blanc benchmark with citrus, herbs, and real mineral cut. This is the bottle to buy when you want the grape at its most precise and food-friendly.</p>
    </div>
